#: {{ux|fr|The Shadows est un groupe '''pionnier''' du rock britannique.|The Shadows were a '''pioneering''' British rock group.}}
# first to [[colonize]]
#: {{ux|fr|La végétation '''pionnière''' est le premier type de végétation colonisant un milieu.|'''Pioneer''' vegetation is the first type of vegetation to colonize an environment.}}

====Descendants====
[[File:Young Pioneers in Kazakh SSR.jpg|thumb|Des '''pionniers''' kazakhs.]]
The French word was borrowed in Russian, {{l|ru|пионер}}, which in turn, through the influence of the Communist superpower, was widely adopted throughout Europe in the sense of [[young pioneer]]; the list below traces both direct (from French) and indirect (via Russian) borrowings.
